As a compliance requirement, there is a 60 days policy-lock feature in iView, where in users who have not logged into application since last 60 days or more, their IDs in IView application will be locked at databases level.

Users can unlock the IDs by raising an unlock id request in LAM for application "I-VIEW".

Once the LAM for ID unlock is Approved & Closed then you can try to login in the I-View application same day or Next day before 11:00 AM or else the ID will be again locked.

Does it resolve your issue?
